cat << EOF
Ethtool is a Linux net driver diagnostic and tuning tool for the
Linux 2.4.x (or later) series of kernels. It obtains information
and diagnostics related to media, link status, driver version,
PCI (or other) bus location, and more. Ethtool obsoletes mii-tool.
